content = I Class (none awarded)
II Class (1 awarded):
&lt;U+2022&gt; General Jan Skrzynecki (for the battles of Wawer and D&lt;U+0119&gt;be Wielkie)
III Class (105 awarded)
IV Class (1794 awarded)
